---
import Basic from "../layouts/Basic.astro";
---

<Basic title="Kfir's Portfolio">
  <section class="relative pb-6">
    <div class="bg-hero-bg absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center z-[-1] blur-xl">
    </div>
    <div
      class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center py-96">
      <h1
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-rose-400 light-shades font-Bebas tracking-widest cursor-pointer text-5xl text-center transition-all duration-[5s] xl:hover:scale-y-[1.25] xl:hover:scale-x-[1.35] lg:text-8xl">
        Proffesional Website Developer
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    class="relative bg-gradient-to-t from-transparent dark:via-bk-dark-shades via-bkl-dark-shades">
    <div
      class="container flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-12 pt-12 pb-32 gap-12 text-center">
      <h3 class="dark:text-bk-light-shades text-bkl-light-shades text-3xl">
        ABOUT
      </h3>
      <div
        class="dark:text-bk-light-shades text-bkl-light-shades text-start w-fit lg:w-[80em]">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-Outfit">Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Allow me to introduce myself. My name is Kfir, and I am a passionate
          and experienced developer hailing from the beautiful country of
          Israel. I am thrilled to offer my expertise as a versatile programmer,
          with proficiency in various programming languages and a wide range of
          development skills.
        </p>
        <br />
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-Outfit">Background and Journey</h2>
        <p>
          My journey in the world of programming began with C#. I dived into the
          realm of game development, utilizing the power of Unity to create
          captivating and immersive gaming experiences. This initial venture
          sparked my curiosity and drive to explore further possibilities within
          the programming landscape.
        </p>
        <p>
          Eager to expand my repertoire, I ventured into Java, where I undertook
          various software projects, honing my problem-solving skills and
          developing a strong foundation in application development. With each
          project, I deepened my understanding of the intricacies of coding,
          solidifying my commitment to continuous learning and improvement.
        </p>
        <p>
          However, I soon realized that the realm of programming was far more
          expansive than I initially thought. Driven by my thirst for knowledge,
          I delved into the vast realm of web development and front-end design.
          Through meticulous learning and hands-on experience, I acquired
          expertise in JavaScript and front-end development frameworks,
          equipping me with the ability to create visually stunning and
          user-friendly websites.
        </p>
        <p>
          As I delved deeper into the world of front-end development, I
          discovered the symbiotic relationship between the front-end and
          backend. Determined to master this holistic approach, I embarked on a
          journey to unravel the complexities of backend development. I immersed
          myself in the study of Linux, navigating its intricacies and learning
          to harness its power to build robust and scalable backend systems.
          Through this endeavor, I achieved a comprehensive understanding of the
          entire development process, from crafting beautiful front-end
          experiences to engineering robust backend architectures.
        </p>
        <br />
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-Outfit">Skills and Expertise</h2>
        <p>
          Today, as a seasoned developer, I bring my wealth of knowledge and
          diverse skill set to each project I undertake. From front-end
          development to full stack implementation, I am well-versed in crafting
          elegant and efficient solutions tailored to meet the unique
          requirements of each client.
        </p>
        <p>
          When you choose to work with me, you can expect meticulous attention
          to detail, a dedication to delivering high-quality results, and a
          commitment to constant growth and innovation. I pride myself on my
          ability to adapt to the ever-evolving technology landscape and stay
          ahead of the curve.
        </p>
        <br />
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-Outfit">Let&#39;s Collaborate!</h2>
        <p>
          So whether you need a captivating website, a robust application, or a
          seamless integration of front-end and backend systems, I am here to
          turn your vision into reality. Let&#39;s embark on a collaborative
          journey and bring your ideas to life.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for considering my services. I look forward to the
          opportunity to work with you and contribute to your success.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Basic>
